{
  "texts": [
    "It has been a prominent aspect of the public discussion of AI and was selected as Cambridge dictionary's word of the year (Creamer, 2023).",
    "Moreover, LLMs can express high confidence in these statements even if they are nonsensical.",
    "One reason for LLMs' susceptibility to hallucinations is the training data consisting of a large corpus of text and code, which can contain errors and inconsistencies.",
    "When an LLM is generating text, it may draw on this information in unexpected ways, leading to hallucinations (Ye et al., 2023; Zhang et al., 2023).",
    "Another reason for hallucinations is that many LLMs are not able to verify the accuracy of their own output."
  ]
}